The dancer climbs the stage and you can see the subtle curves of her body. She is wearing only silky red underwear that doesn't leave much to the imagination. She dances on and off the pole for a few minutes before facing you and slowly makes her way toward your booth.

She approaches the glass doorway, her face obscured by her hair. She turns away from you and slowly bends over to grab the ticket on the floor.

The beautiful woman slowly straightens her back and turns again to face you.
